After all the searching, I couldn't find text that was fixed (and not grey), and backgrounds that look cute, so I decided to make one for myself!

Yes, you can use the code! Credit me if you'd like.

If there are any problems, feel free to comment them.

P.S: It looks wayy better with light mode on then dark mode.
